{"type":"miscellaneous","title":"Eternia Crystal","summaries":["The <b>Eternia Crystal</b> is an event-summoning item. When used in the Eternia Crystal Stand, the Old One's Army event begins. The Eternia Crystal is purchased from the Tavernkeep for <span class=\"coin\" title=\"25 Silver Coins\" data-sort-value=\"2500\"><span class=\"sc\">25</span></span> (pre-mechanical bosses), <span class=\"coin\" title=\"1 Gold Coin\" data-sort-value=\"10000\"><span class=\"gc\">1</span></span> (post-mechanical bosses), or <span class=\"coin\" title=\"4 Gold Coins\" data-sort-value=\"40000\"><span class=\"gc\">4</span></span> (post-Golem)."],"statistics":{"Consumable":"<span class=\"t-yes\">✔️</span>","Tooltip":"<i><span class=\"gameText\">Place in the Eternia Crystal Stand to summon Etheria's portals</span></i>","Rarity":"<span class=\"rarity\">[img:Rarity level: 3]</span>","Buy":"T1: <span class=\"coin\" title=\"25 Silver Coins\" data-sort-value=\"2500\"><span class=\"sc\">25</span></span><br>T2: <span class=\"coin\" title=\"1 Gold Coin\" data-sort-value=\"10000\"><span class=\"gc\">1</span></span><br>T3: <span class=\"coin\" title=\"4 Gold Coins\" data-sort-value=\"40000\"><span class=\"gc\">4</span></span>","Sell":"T1: <span class=\"coin\" title=\"5 Silver Coins\" data-sort-value=\"500\"><span class=\"sc\">5</span></span><br>T2: <span class=\"coin\" title=\"20 Silver Coins\" data-sort-value=\"2000\"><span class=\"sc\">20</span></span><br>T3: <span class=\"coin\" title=\"80 Silver Coins\" data-sort-value=\"8000\"><span class=\"sc\">80</span></span>","Research":"<abbr class=\"journey\" title=\"Journey Mode\">3 required</abbr>"},"crafts":{}}